{"tid":1417131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口號需要文宣！！文宣去哂邊！","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:16:54.000Z","uid":176449,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1107b3cb46e2178e1a32c319dc3df93299bfeb3","tid":1417131,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n依兩句根本冇問題<br />\n<br />\n係 確實有人會唔鍾意依兩句<br />\n但係係因為我地冇足夠嘅文宣<br />\n去同市民講依兩句嘅意思<br />\n<br />\n所以我地需要做嘅唔係改口號<br />\n而係宣傳個口號嘅意思<br />\n我地需要文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去幫手整啲圖出嚟<br />\n唔好令市民俾林鄭誤導！<br />\n<br />\n同埋想講嘅係 深夜post真係好on9<br />\n愛國都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家諗清楚先正皮啦<br />\n到時人地聽到我地話愛國 <br />\n真係會覺得我哋講緊香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a441a9100ca6b98a4bd6d8003df31de798e65d","tid":1417131,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"854f1f4f583e24634060935ca7e41b4f4fb65dc3","tid":1417131,"uid":176449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"不過要繼續講五大訴求<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為好緊要！</span>"},{"pid":"f6b4ee1534622c07fc954b56185f3948190fcaab","tid":1417131,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7d11eb98d194e9d6b00ce3e726fab85d6a4cd2e","tid":1417131,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"推到十連"},{"pid":"2c638dbe2fa68d6c37d4afc87838be95f80b70aa","tid":1417131,"uid":176449,"like":0,"disli